{"id":268084,"type":3,"name":"A's×Darling ドラマCD","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/10/08/268084_K63Z0.jpg","summary":"人気モデルで、仲のいい四人――太一、千草、羽鳥、志狼。\r\n彼らは大学に通いながら、仕事に、恋に、忙しくも順風満帆な日々を過ごしていた。\r\n\r\n毎日が楽しくて、なにより、キミのことが大好き!\r\nなのに……どうして時々不安になっちゃうんだろ?\r\n\r\n「3のつく時期は恋愛の節目、ってよく言うよね」\r\n\r\n3日、3週間、3ヶ月、3年――。\r\n彼らの前に立ちはだかる、目には見えない「3」のハードル。\r\n\r\nだけど俺は、絶対に乗り越えたいんだ。\r\nキミと、一緒に。","info":"<li><span>艺术家: </span><a href=\"/person/5872\">江口拓也</a> / <a href=\"/person/12483\">古川慎</a> / <a href=\"/person/5151\">佐藤拓也</a> / <a href=\"/person/5121\">前野智昭</a></li><li><span>插图: </span><a href=\"/person/36465\">秋鹿ユギリ</a></li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2018-11-28</li><li><span>价格: </span>￥ 3,240</li><li><span>碟片数量: </span>1</li><li><span>厂牌: </span>ティームエンタテインメント</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"古川慎","count":1},{"name":"佐藤拓也","count":1},{"name":"江口拓也","count":1},{"name":"前野智昭","count":1},{"name":"drama","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":5872,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f6/f1/5872_prsn_xZiFZ.jpg","name":"江口拓也","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":5121,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8d/35/5121_prsn_6732U.jpg","name":"前野智昭","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":12483,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/15/71/12483_prsn_pXYzu.jpg","name":"古川慎","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":5151,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4f/15/5151_prsn_b2sI9.jpg","name":"佐藤拓也","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":36465,"image":"","name":"秋鹿ユギリ","desc":"插图"}],"relations":[{"id":273484,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/af/de/273484_ClHcx.jpg","title":"A's×Darling TYPE.2 猫谷千草","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/273484"},{"id":277103,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/8b/e6/277103_uiL1R.jpg","title":"A's×Darling TYPE.1 犬塚太一","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/277103"},{"id":277104,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f2/5b/277104_BwTjz.jpg","title":"A's×Darling TYPE.3 七海羽鳥","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/277104"}]}